<D>__{nine hundred thousand!? it's a white collar charge.}
<C>__{attorney}
<D>__{your honor }
<A>__{the judge begins filling out a form. he barely looks up at them.}
<C>__{houston judge}
<D>__{mister russell is a flight risk. the bond is set. nine hundred thousand.}
<C>__{steven}
<D>__{this is bullshit.}
<P>__{(sotto to attorney)}
<D>__{set a reduction hearing.}
<C>__{attorney}
<P>__{(off this)}
<D>__{your honor we'd like to set a reduction hearing.}
<C>__{houston judge}
